<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 12:28:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>解说：欧盟调查中国制造的电动汽车接下来会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/what-happens-next-china-made-evs-investigated-by-eu-2024-10-03/</link><description>欧盟成员国将于周五就欧盟委员会对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税的提案进行投票。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/what-happens-next-china-made-evs-investigated-by-eu-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis首席执行官表示，Stellantis与雷诺合并的传言“纯粹是猜测”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/rumours-stellantis-renault-merger-are-pure-speculation-says-stellantis-ceo-2024-10-03/</link><description>Stellantis 首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯 (Carlos Tavares) 周四在参观这家法国-意大利汽车制造商位于法国东部的中心之一时表示，有关 Stellantis 和雷诺合并的传言“纯粹是猜测”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:12:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/rumours-stellantis-renault-merger-are-pure-speculation-says-stellantis-ceo-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利外交部长将否决欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hungary-will-veto-eu-plan-impose-chinese-ev-tariffs-foreign-minister-2024-10-03/</link><description>匈牙利外交部长彼得·西雅尔托(Peter Szijjarto)周四在其Facebook页面上表示，匈牙利将否决一项欧盟提议，该提议旨在对中国制造的电动汽车(EV)进口征收高达45%的关税，因为该计划“有害且危险”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:40:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hungary-will-veto-eu-plan-impose-chinese-ev-tariffs-foreign-minister-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾严肃对待外国在该国从事间谍活动的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-takes-allegations-foreign-spying-country-seriously-2024-10-03/</link><description>菲律宾周四对媒体报道称外国在该国进行秘密行动表示担忧，并表示正在与相关机构协调解决此事。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:35:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-takes-allegations-foreign-spying-country-seriously-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称法国CCF银行将裁员1000多人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/french-retail-bank-ccf-plans-shed-more-than-1000-jobs-sources-say-2024-10-03/</link><description>三位工会消息人士周四告诉路透社，法国零售银行法国商业信贷银行 (CCF) 在投资公司 Cerberus Capital Management 的支持下，计划裁员 1,000 多人，约占其员工总数的三分之一。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:10:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/french-retail-bank-ccf-plans-shed-more-than-1000-jobs-sources-say-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：随着欧洲和日本鹰派的呼声，美元飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-03/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，随着美国限制的临近，中国药明康德探索出售制药业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-wuxi-explores-sale-pharma-units-us-restrictions-loom-ft-reports-2024-10-03/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周四报道，在美国以国家安全为由针对中国生物科技公司之后，药明康德和药明生物正计划出售部分业务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 09:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-wuxi-explores-sale-pharma-units-us-restrictions-loom-ft-reports-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>香港零售业面临挑战，8 月份销售额下降 10%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hong-kong-sees-challenges-retail-sector-august-sales-fall-10-2024-10-03/</link><description>政府数据显示，香港8月份零售额同比下降10.1%，反映出港元相对坚挺、居民消费模式的变化以及假期出国旅游的增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 09:24:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hong-kong-sees-challenges-retail-sector-august-sales-fall-10-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>精神焕发的阿尔卡拉斯渴望参加上海大师赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/refreshed-alcaraz-raring-go-shanghai-masters-2024-10-03/</link><description>世界排名第二的卡洛斯·阿尔卡拉斯表示，作为球队的一员参加戴维斯杯和拉沃尔杯让他感觉焕然一新，并做好了参加亚洲赛的准备，他希望在中国公开赛的胜利基础上再夺上海大师赛冠军。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 07:34:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/refreshed-alcaraz-raring-go-shanghai-masters-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，新兴市场货币将在 2024 年剩余时间内保持稳定或削减涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/em-currencies-set-hold-steady-or-pare-gains-rest-2024-2024-10-03/</link><description>路透调查显示，在美联储抑制了大幅降息的预期后，大多数新兴市场货币将在未来三个月内窄幅波动或削减今年迄今的部分涨幅。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 07:28:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/em-currencies-set-hold-steady-or-pare-gains-rest-2024-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>银行家称，受刺激措施推动，中国企业计划第四季度发行至多150亿美元的海外债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-firms-plan-up-15-bln-overseas-bond-issues-q4-stimulus-boost-say-bankers-2024-10-03/</link><description>财务顾问表示，随着北京的经济刺激措施降低融资成本并刺激借款人的胃口，中国投资级公司本季度准备发行 100 亿至 150 亿美元的离岸债券。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 07:17:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-firms-plan-up-15-bln-overseas-bond-issues-q4-stimulus-boost-say-bankers-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾驱逐两名骚扰亲港活动的中国公民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-deports-two-chinese-nationals-harassing-pro-hong-kong-event-2024-10-03/</link><description>台湾政府周四表示，两名中国公民在中国国庆日骚扰台北香港流亡者的抗议活动后已被驱逐出境。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 05:23:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-deports-two-chinese-nationals-harassing-pro-hong-kong-event-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：采购经理人指数为降息铺平道路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-03/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 04:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>全球股市下跌，油价因中东冲突进一步上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-03/</link><description>由于欧洲和亚洲股指周四普遍回落，全球股市下跌，而由于市场权衡中东冲突扩大的风险，油价进一步上涨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 02:15:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>中方敦促安理会缓和中东危机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-un-security-council-de-escalate-middle-east-crisis-2024-10-03/</link><description>随着以色列对黎巴嫩发动新的空袭，中国呼吁联合国安理会采取“紧急行动”，缓和中东局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 02:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-un-security-council-de-escalate-middle-east-crisis-2024-10-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>